snippet.title: Kind Words (lo fi chill beats to write to)
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1070710/Kind_Words_lo_fi_chill_beats_to_write_to/
https://www.humblebundle.com/monthly/p/july_2019_monthly

Write nice letters to people and trade stickers! 

A game by Popcannibal.

Has something got you down? Stressed you out? It might help you to talk about it. Write out your concerns and sorrows and share them. Everyone can respond to requests with letters of comfort, sympathy or gentle advice. Use your words to lift others and be lifted in return.

Music:
can i be part of your life? by Barradeen | https://soundcloud.com/barradeen
Music promoted by https://www.free-stock-music.com
